vgp - Video Get Podcasts

USAGE:
    vgp

DESCRIPTION:
    Display metadata for all downloaded audio-only files (podcasts). Shows information
    about each audio file including title, duration, uploader, and date.

EXAMPLES:
    vgp

NOTES:
    This command only shows audio-only files (where extract_audio=1).
    Use vg to see video files only.
